name: Ghost Girl #01
description:
This is the first in a series of Ghost Girls that I will be releasing. Aubrey is her name and not much is known about her. She haunts a newly developed area that was previously an old fishing village. She mostly sticks to the outside of homes, peeking in windows. If you leave a plate of crackers on your doorstep she will respond in kind by making all of the flowers in your garden bloom.
